#: source/soundWave_lib/main.py:2152
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Orpheus rendering requires switching NVDA temporarily to a fallback synthesizer, but switching to '{fallback_synth}' failed.\n"
"\n"
"Please ensure at least one non-Orpheus NVDA synthesizer is available, then try again."
