#: source/soundWave_lib/main.py:2231
msgid ""
"SoundWave could not find the installed Eloquence/IBMTTS speech engine.\n"
"\n"
"Install or update the Eloquence or IBMTTS NVDA add-on, reload NVDA, then try again."
msgstr ""
"SoundWave nemohol nájsť nainštalovaný rečový engine Eloquence/IBMTTS.\n"
"\n"
"Nainštalujte alebo aktualizujte doplnok Eloquence alebo IBMTTS pre NVDA, znovu načítajte NVDA a skúste to znova."

